    This event is used to indicate a change in the state of a bound SolQueueReceiver. The state can alter between ActiveFlowIndicationEvent.FLOW_INACTIVE and ActiveFlowIndicationEvent.FLOW_ACTIVE Such events can occur upon starting a SolQueueReceiver, due to changes in underlying connection state or due to events indicated from the router.
